INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (11, 1, '记录下今天用uniapp开发小程序的小问题', 'uniapp', 1616371200000, 10, '<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">1.今天用uniapp开发小程序遇到一个小问题，本来在h5调试好好的可以获取到vuex的变量，没想到小程序调试vuex的变量变成了&#x60;undefined&#x60;。这让我很是懵逼，然后看了uniapp社区才知道，小程序拿不到深层的数据，那怎么解决呢。这是可以用到计算属性了</p><pre><code><span style=\"color:#c678dd\">import</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\"> { </span><span style=\"color:#e06c75\">Component</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">, </span><span style=\"color:#e06c75\">Vue</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\"> } </span><span style=\"color:#c678dd\">from</span> <span style=\"color:#98c379\">&#x27;vue-property-decorator&#x27;</span> <br/><span style=\"color:#c678dd\">import</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\"> { </span><span style=\"color:#e06c75\">App</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\"> } </span><span style=\"color:#c678dd\">from</span> <span style=\"color:#98c379\">&#x27;@/store&#x27;</span><br/><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">@</span><span style=\"color:#61afef\">Component</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">({</span><br/> <span style=\"color:#e06c75\">name</span><span style=\"color:#56b6c2\">:</span> <span style=\"color:#98c379\">&#x27;Home&#x27;</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">,</span><br/> <span style=\"color:#e06c75\">components</span><span style=\"color:#56b6c2\">:</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\"> {</span><br/><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">    wave,</span><br/><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">  },</span><br/><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">})</span><br/><span style=\"color:#c678dd\">export</span> <span style=\"color:#e06c75\">default</span> <span style=\"color:#c678dd\">class</span> <span style=\"color:#e5c07b\">Home</span> <span style=\"color:#c678dd\">extends</span> <span style=\"color:#e5c07b\">Vue</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\"> {</span><br/>  <span style=\"color:#56b6c2\">get</span> <span style=\"color:#61afef\">isShow</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\"> () {</span><br/>     <span style=\"color:#c678dd\">return</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\"> App.</span><span style=\"color:#e06c75\">isShow</span><br/>  <span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">}</span><br/> <br/>  <span style=\"color:#56b6c2\">set</span> <span style=\"color:#61afef\">isShow</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">(v </span><span style=\"color:#56b6c2\">:</span> <span style=\"color:#56b6c2\">boolean</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">) {  </span><br/><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">    </span> <span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">App.</span><span style=\"color:#61afef\">changisShow</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">(</span><span style=\"color:#e06c75\">v</span><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">)</span><br/>  <span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">}</span><br/><span style=\"color:#abb2bf\">}</span></code></pre><p></p><p>上述双向绑定要用到setter[Vue warn]: Computed property &quot;CurrentStep&quot; was assigned to but it has no setter.</p><p></p><p>2.当使用到uviewui的button组件时，@tap我记得在h5跟app端都是使用正常的，但是在小程序确失灵了。查看uview文档看到😤</p><div class=\"media-wrap image-wrap\"><img class=\"media-wrap image-wrap\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"/></div><p></p>', 1, 'https://www.wsw2000.top:7001/public/upload/20210324/1616575274632.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (12, 3, '博客升级为https啦', 'ssl,https', 1616544000000, 15, '## 前台\n\n1. 首先除了`node_modules`文件夹，其他的都上传到服务器上1.我是通过这个[https://letsencrypt.osfipin.com](https://letsencrypt.osfipin.com/)来申请的免费ssl证书，按照他里面的步骤一般都能申请成功的吧。由于我是配置nginx服务器的，所以不止在宝塔添加其他证书，还配置了nginx，如下![image](data:image/png;base64,)\n\n2.然后配置nginx：\n\n```javascript\n\nserver\n{\n    listen 80;\n    listen 443 ssl http2;\n    ssl_certificate \"path\\fullchain.crt\" \n    ssl_certificate_key \"path\\private.pem\"\n    ssl_protocols TLSv1.1 TLSv1.2;\n    ssl_ciphers ECDHE-RSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256:HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5:!RC4:!DHE;\n    ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;\n    ssl_session_cache shared:SSL:10m;\n    ssl_session_timeout 10m;\n}  \n```\n\n\n## eggjs配置https\n\n在config目录下新建个config.prod.js文件，当执行npm run start 进去生产模式才会执行，这里详细可看官方文档[https://eggjs.org/zh-cn/basics/config.html](https://eggjs.org/zh-cn/basics/config.html) ，然后新增\n\n```javascript\n// https\n  config.cluster = {\n    https: {\n      key: \'/private.key\',\n      cert: \'/fullchain.crt\',\n    },\n  };\n```\n\n由于https默认是443端口，所以我们的start命令可换成`\"start\": \"egg-scripts start --daemon --prot=443\"`\n\n## 后台https\n\n我的后台管理系统是我用express服务器搭的，本人能力有限，目前https就指向3000端口，http则是另外一个端口，可能后续会改进，但是我觉得也没必要，目前就博主一个人使用，哈哈哈😁\n\n```javascript\nvar express = require(\'express\');\nvar https = require(\'https\');\nvar http = require(\'http\');\nvar fs = require(\'fs\');\n\n//同步读取密钥和签名证书\nvar options = {\n    key:fs.readFileSync(\'./private.pem\',\'utf-8\'),\n    cert:fs.readFileSync(\'./fullchain.crt\',\'utf-8\')\n};\nvar app = express();\nvar httpsServer = https.createServer(options,app);\nvar httpServer = http.createServer(app);\n\napp.use(express.static(\'./build\'))\napp.get(\'/\',function(req,res,next){\n    res.send(\'Hello Express+https\');\n});\n//https监听3000端口\nhttpsServer.listen(3000);\n//http监听8088端口\nhttpServer.listen(8088);\n```\n', 1, 'https://www.wsw2000.top:7001/public/upload/20210324/1616589341272.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (13, 1, 'TypeScript学习笔记二', 'TypeScript', 1616803200000, 7, '## Es6的类\n\n1. `class`是`es6`才有的，TypeScript 除了实现了所有 ES6 中的类的功能以外，还添加了一些新的用法。先来复习下类的基本写法：\n\n```javascript\nclass Animal {\n  public name\n  constructor(name){\n    this.name = name\n  }\n  getName(){\n    return \'hello animal\'\n  }\n}\n\nclass Cat extends Animal {\n  public skill\n  constructor(name,skill){\n    super(name)\n    this.skill = skill\n  }\n  getSkill() {\n    return `${this.skill}`\n  }\n}\n\nconst car = new Cat(\'cat\',\'eat\')\nconsole.log(car.getSkill());  //eat\nconsole.log(car.getName());   // hello animal\n\n\n```\n\n上述中，子类继承父类 `Animal`要用 `super()`来调用父类的构造函数和方法。\n\n2.getter跟setter\n\n```javascript\nclass Peason {\n  constructor(name) {\n    this.name = name;\n  }\n  get name() {\n    return \'Jack\';\n  }\n  set name(value) {\n    console.log(\'setter: \' + value);\n  }\n}\n\nlet a = new Peason(\'Kitty\'); // setter: Kitty\na.name = \'Tom\'; // setter: Tom\nconsole.log(a.name); // Jack\n```\n\n3.静态方法 : 使用 `static` 修饰符修饰的方法称为静态方法，直接通过类来调用,实例化会报错 ：\n\n```javascript\nclass Animal {\n  static isAnimal(a) {\n    return a instanceof Animal\n  }\n}\n\nlet a = new Animal()\nconsole.log(Animal.isAnimal(a))// true\n// a.isAnimal(a); // TypeError: a.isAnimal is not a function\n```\n\n## ES7的类\n\n1.ES6 中实例的属性只能通过构造函数中的 `this.xxx` 来定义，ES7 提案中可以直接在类里面定义\n\n2.可以使用 `static` 定义一个静态属性\n\n```javascript\nclass Animal {\n  name = \'Jack\';\n\n  constructor() {\n    // ...\n  }\n}\n\nlet a = new Animal();\nconsole.log(a.name); // Jack\n\nclass Animal {\n  static num = 42;\n\n  constructor() {\n    // ...\n  }\n}\n\nconsole.log(Animal.num); // 42\n```\n\n## TypeScript 中类的用法\n\nTypeScript 可以使用三种访问修饰符（Access Modifiers），分别是 `public`、`private` 和 `protected`。\n\n* `public` 修饰的属性或方法是公有的，可以在任何地方被访问到，默认所有的属性和方法都是`public` 的\n* `private` 修饰的属性或方法是私有的，不能在声明它的类的外部访问\n* `protected` 修饰的属性或方法是受保护的，它和`private` 类似，区别是它在子类中也是允许被访问的\n\n比如：\n\n```javascript\n\nclass Animal {\n  public name;\n  public constructor(name) {\n    this.name = name;\n  }\n}\n\nlet a = new Animal(\'Jack\');\nconsole.log(a.name); // Jack\na.name = \'Tom\';\nconsole.log(a.name); // Tom\n```\n\n上述我们用了 `public`是可以直接访问实例的 `name` 属性，而如果用了 `private`的话\n\n```javascript\nclass Animal {\n  private name;\n  public constructor(name) {\n    this.name = name;\n  }\n}\n\nlet a = new Animal(\'Jack\');\nconsole.log(a.name);\n//此时编辑器就会提示属性“name”为私有属性，只能在类“Animal”中访问。ts(2341)\n```\n\n而且使用 `private` 修饰的属性或方法，在子类中也是不允许访问的：\n\n```javascript\nclass Animal {\n  private name;\n  public constructor(name) {\n    this.name = name;\n  }\n}\n\nclass Cat extends Animal {\n  constructor(name) {\n    super(name);\n    console.log(this.name); //属性“name”为私有属性，只能在类“Animal”中访问。ts(2341)\n  }\n}\n\n```\n\n而如果是用 `protected` 修饰，则允许在子类中访问：\n\n```javascript\n\nclass Animal {\n  protected name;\n  public constructor(name) {\n    this.name = name;\n  }\n}\n\nclass Cat extends Animal {\n  constructor(name) {\n    super(name);\n    console.log(this.name);\n  }\n}\n```\n\n同理，当构造函数修饰为 `private` 时，该类不允许被继承或者实例化，而当构造函数修饰为 `protected` 时，该类只允许被继承\n\n```javascript\nclass Animal {\n  public name;\n  protected constructor(name) {\n    this.name = name;\n  }\n}\nclass Cat extends Animal {\n  constructor(name) {\n    super(name);\n  }\n}\n\nlet a = new Animal(\'Jack\');   // 类“Animal”的构造函数是受保护的，仅可在类声明中访问。ts(2674)\nlet cat = new Cat(\'Jack\');\n```\n\n所以 `private私有的`跟 `protected保护的`一样可在类声明中访问，但是 `protected`可以被继承子类使用\n\n### 参数属性\n\n可以这么写：\n\n```javascript\nclass Animal {\n  // public name: string;\n  public constructor(public name) {\n    // this.name = name;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### readonly\n\n```javascript\nclass Animal {\n  // public readonly name;\n  public constructor(public readonly name) {\n    // this.name = name;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### abstract\n\n```javascript\nabstract class Animal {\n  public name;\n  public constructor(name) {\n    this.name = name;\n  }\n  public abstract sayHi();\n}\n\nlet a = new Animal(\'Jack\');   // 无法创建抽象类的实例。ts(2511)\n```\n\n其次，抽象类中的抽象方法必须被子类实现,且无法通过 super 表达式访问“Animal”类中的“sayHi”抽象方法\n\n```javascript\nabstract class Animal {\n  public name;\n  public constructor(name) {\n    this.name = name;\n  }\n  public abstract sayHi();\n}\n\nclass Cat extends Animal {\n  constructor(name){\n    super(name)\n  \n  }\n  public eat() {\n    super.sayHi()  // 无法通过 super 表达式访问“Animal”类中的“sayHi”抽象方法。\n    console.log(`${this.name} is eating.`);\n  }\n  public sayHi() {\n    console.log(`Meow, My name is ${this.name}`);\n  }\n}\n\nlet cat = new Cat(\'Tom\');\n```\n\n给类加上 TypeScript 的类型很简单，与接口类似：\n\n```javascript\n\nclass Animal {\n  name: string;\n  constructor(name: string) {\n    this.name = name;\n  }\n  sayHi(): string {\n    return `My name is ${this.name}`;\n  }\n}\n\nlet a: Animal = new Animal(\'Jack\');\nconsole.log(a.sayHi()); // My name is Jack\n```\n\n## 类实现接口\n\n举例来说，门是一个类，防盗门是门的子类。如果防盗门有一个报警器的功能，我们可以简单的给防盗门添加一个报警方法。这时候如果有另一个类，车，也有报警器的功能，就可以考虑把报警器提取出来，作为一个接口，防盗门和车都去实现它：\n\n```javascript\ninterface Alarm {\n    alert(): void;\n}\n\nclass Door {\n}\n\nclass SecurityDoor extends Door implements Alarm {\n    alert() {\n        console.log(\'SecurityDoor alert\');\n    }\n}\n\nclass Car implements Alarm {\n    alert() {\n        console.log(\'Car alert\');\n    }\n}\n```\n\n一个类可以实现多个接口：\n\n```javascript\n\ninterface Alarm {\n    alert(): void;\n}\n\ninterface Light {\n    lightOn(): void;\n    lightOff(): void;\n}\n\nclass Car implements Alarm, Light {\n    alert() {\n        console.log(\'Car alert\');\n    }\n    lightOn() {\n        console.log(\'Car light on\');\n    }\n    lightOff() {\n        console.log(\'Car light off\');\n    }\n}\n//Car 实现了 Alarm 和 Light 接口，既能报警，也能开关车灯\n```\n\n## 接口继承接口\n\n```javascript\ninterface Alarm {\n    alert(): void;\n}\n\ninterface LightableAlarm extends Alarm {\n    lightOn(): void;\n    lightOff(): void;\n}\n```\n\n\n\n\n## 接口继承类\n\n常见的面向对象语言中，接口是不能继承类的，但是在 TypeScript 中却是可以的：\n\n```javascript\nclass Point {\n    x: number;\n    y: number;\n    constructor(x: number, y: number) {\n        this.x = x;\n        this.y = y;\n    }\n}\n\ninterface Point3d extends Point {\n    z: number;\n}\n\nlet point3d: Point3d = {x: 1, y: 2, z: 3};\n```\n\n我感觉这个接口继承类对于我会很少用到，但既然学习了，就记下笔记把😄\n', 1, 'https://ss1.bdstatic.com/70cFuXSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=3999732859,2371212932&fm=26&gp=0.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (14, 1, 'nodemailer实现留言邮箱提醒', '邮箱提醒', 1617408000000, 3, '1.首先  `yarn add nodemailer`  然后在config的config.default.js里面定义 `config.nodemailer = require(\'nodemailer\')`\n\n2.在service里面创建sendEamil.js \n\n```javascript\n\n\'use strict\';\nconst Service = require(\'egg\').Service;\nclass sendService extends Service {\n  sendMail(address,name,form, subject, html) {\n    //下面这几个改成你自己的邮箱、昵称和授权码\n    const user = \"xxx@QQ.COM\";\n    const pass = \'xxx\' //授权码在QQ邮箱设置-账号-开启服务：POP3/SMTP服务（详情参考https://service.mail.qq.com/cgi-bin/help?subtype=1&&id=28&&no=1001256）\n    this.config.nodemailer.createTransport({host: \"smtp.qq.com\", auth: {user, pass}}).sendMail({\n        from: `${name}<${form}>`,//发送者\n        to:user,//收件人邮箱，多个邮箱地址间用英文逗号隔开\n        subject:`来自${address}的${name}来${subject}`,//邮件主题\n        html//支持html\n    }, err => err && console.log(\"邮件发送失败： \", err));\n  }\n}\n\nmodule.exports = sendService;\n```\n\n3.在发表评论的接口里面直接调用\n\n```javascript\n      this.ctx.service.sendEmail.sendMail(info.address,info.unamed,\'xxx@qq.com\',`${info.article_id == -1 ? \'留言\' :`评论文章${info.article_id}`}`,info.content);//发送邮件\n\n```\n\n这样简单的留言评论邮箱提醒就完成了，但是这里面*发送者的qq邮箱只能是跟授权码绑定的qq邮箱一样*😄\n', 0, 'https://tva4.sinaimg.cn/large/9bd9b167gy1g2rkqj69uqj21c00u07co.jpg');

